Calculates confidence limits for imposex time seriesl

Source: R/proportional_odds_functions.R
ctsm.VDS.cl.Rd

Calculates confidence limits for imposex time seriesl

Usage

ctsm.VDS.cl(fit, nsim = 1000)

Arguments

fit

The output from a call to ctsm.VDS.index.opt (sort of)

nsim

The number of simulations on which each set of confidence limits is based; default 1000
